show.description: She loved him, married him, and woke up to find him gone. Now, after eight long years, Meher Chaudhary returns fearless, fierce, and ready to confront Arjun Singh Rathore. But in this high-stakes game of lies and loyalty, nothing is as it seems. Watch Now!
